description: Briefly explained, sonification means to transform data into sound with the purpose of conveying information. In this talk, I will explain how sonification could serve as a supporting tool for cardiac diagnosis and monitoring, and how you could use Python to create sonifications from electrocardiogram (ECG) data. 
